metadata.name: Sunset Melancholy
metadata.description:
Beautiful sunsets often induce a feeling of melancholy inside me. 

I feel small and insignificant in this vast universe, and begin to question life and my purpose. 

However, these same thoughts and feelings overwhelm me with a sense of wonder and beauty - and I understand how lucky I am to be here, experiencing this life. 


Sunset Melancholy 
4320 x 7680 px
ytopp 2022
1/1
